Package: peakrefine
Type: Package
Title: Peak Refinement Metric Gathering and Evalutation by Motif Enrichment
Version: 0.0.0
Authors@R: person("Joseph R", "Boyd", email = "jrboyd@uvm.edu",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Gather cross-strand-correlation per peak and other more
    common metrics.  Evaluates metric power with motif enrichment via
    PWMEnrich package.
